thailand-visa-asia-2025-9%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20back%20to%20Bangkok%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20opened%20a%20fashion%20boutique.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sutasit%20Srivisarvacha%2C%2030%2C%20a%20Thai%20UC%20San%20Diego%20graduate%20who%20moved%20back%20to%20Bangkok.%20His%20words%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20getting%20sent%20off%20to%20boarding%20school%20was%20always%20the%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20path%20my%20parents%20had%20taken.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20experience%20life%20beyond%20Thailand%20and%20develop%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2013%2C%20I%20started%20my%20first%20year%20of%20prep%20school%20on%20Vancouver%20Island%20in%20Canada.%20I%20hated%20it%20and%20felt%20homesick.%20I'd%20call%20home%20crying%20to%20my%20parents%20all%20the%20time.%20The%20weather%20sucked%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20thinking%20how%20ridiculous%20it%20was%20to%20eat%20rice%20with%20a%20knife%20and%20fork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20my%20last%20two%20years%2C%20when%20I%20finally%20got%20a%20good%20roommate.%20Life%20got%20easier.%20I%20started%20finding%20my%20own%20community%2C%20got%20into%20basketball%2C%20and%20slowly%20stopped%20fighting%20the%20reality%20that%20I%20was%20there%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20for%20college%2C%20I%20only%20applied%20to%20schools%20in%20California%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20Texas%20because%20I%20was%20done%20with%20the%20cold.%20I%20ended%20up%20at%20UC%20San%20Diego%20studying%20social%20psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%2C%20it%20didn't%20feel%20like%20the%20right%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-back-to-us-after-living-abroad-thailand-regret-home-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20back%20to%20Thailand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20parents%20had%20always%20encouraged%20me%20to%20build%20a%20life%20abroad%2C%20and%20I'd%20internalized%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sutasit%20Srivisarvach%20is%20posing%20on%20a%20bench%20near%20the%20sea%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c12f37f9db348adc0b2d9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESrivisarvach%20was%20inspired%20by%20UX%20Design.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Sutasit%20Srivisarvach%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22477f24a9-7cf4-44b6-af87-d7a9a406cefc%5C%22%3EUX%20design%20in%20California%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20career%20as%20an%20SEO%20analyst%20at%20a%20digital%20marketing%20agency%20in%20San%20Diego.%20I%20found%20the%20work%20boring%2C%20but%20it%20introduced%20me%20to%20UX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20clicked%20immediately%2C%20so%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20to%20attend%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreak-into-tech-quit-teaching-coding-boot-camp-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eonline%20boot%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20be%20a%20user%20experience%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20landed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fux-designer-works-3-jobs-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUX%20designer%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Goji%20Labs%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20a%20small%20digital%20product%20agency%20building%20apps%20and%20websites.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20there%20were%20only%2010%20people%2C%20and%20I%20was%20the%20lone%20designer.%20It%20was%20a%20crash%20course%2C%20cranking%20out%20designs%20across%20multiple%20projects%2C%20but%20I%20loved%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20my%20role%20expanded%20to%20project%20manager%2C%20and%20I%20helped%20build%20the%20entire%20design%20organization%20from%20scr