Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20tangible.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20launching%20a%20fashion%20sportswear%20brand%2C%20but%20retail%20meant%20faster%20revenue%2C%20so%20I%20opened%20a%20men's%20multi-brand%20store%2C%20Fewer%20Better%20Things.%20I%20saw%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market%3A%20Bangkok%20mostly%20offered%20either%20high-end%20designer%20goods%20or%20cheap%20mass-market%20stuff%2C%20with%20little%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sutasit%20Srivisarvacha%20sitting%20in%20Few%20Better%20Things%2C%20a%20shop%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20Thailand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c133f357d362d375e7de2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Sutasit%20Srivisarvacha%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20focuses%20on%20contemporary%20menswear%2C%20home%20d%C3%A9cor%2C%20furniture%2C%20accessories%2C%20bags%2C%20grooming%2C%20and%20art.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20about%20selling%20an%20aesthetic.%20We%20source%20from%20India%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Germany%2C%20Japan%2C%20Korea%2C%20and%20Thailand.%20And%20we%20don't%20have%20an%20online%20catalog.%20I%20want%20people%20to%20be%20intentional%2C%20to%20come%20in%20and%20experience%20the%20pieces%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20set%20aside%204.5%20million%20baht%2C%20or%20about%20%24140%2C000%2C%20of%20my%20own%20savings.%20So%20far%2C%20I've%20spent%203%20million%20baht%2C%20which%20covered%20renovations%2C%20operating%20costs%2C%20salary%20for%20one%20staff%20member%2C%20and%20inventory%20for%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20day%20is%20being%20in%20the%20store%20talking%20to%20customers%20about%20design%2C%20style%2C%20and%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetinee-kingpayome-lukkade-left-america-moved-thailand-beauty-queen-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreative%20energy%20in%20Bangkok%3C%2Fa%3E.%20People%20chase%20the%20things%20they%20enjoy%20and%20don't%20just%20do%20things%20for%20money.%20It's%20nothing%20like%20the%20hustle%20culture%20I%20experienced%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20see%20the%20point%20in%20accumulating%20wealth%20abroad.%20What%20drives%20me%20now%20are%20the%20things%20I%20want%20to%20create%20and%20the%20people%20I%20can%20help.%20If%20I%20ever%20launch%20my%20own%20brand%2C%20the%20products%20will%20be%20made%20in%20Thailand%2C%20by%20Thai%20creators%2C%20so%20it%20can%20generate%20income%20for%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20about%20moving%20to%20Asia%20that%20you%20want%20to%20share%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20editor%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aakarplus%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eakarplus%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-america-moved-to-bangkok-thailand-fashion-fewer-better-things-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757636041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c25394f9db348adc0b4183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-america-moved-to-bangkok-thailand-fashion-fewer-better-things-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20California%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20people%20believed%20tech%20could%20solve%20anything.%20Sutasit%20Srivisarvacha%20didn't%20see%20it%20that%20way%20and%20moved%20back%20to%20Bangkok.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Parisa%20Pichitmarn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-america-moved-to-bangkok-thailand-fashion-fewer-better-things-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22