nd%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20we've%20always%20found%20ways%20to%20stay%20connected.%20Our%20days%20are%20a%20flurry%20of%20links%20and%20photos%2C%20texts%20and%20memes%2C%20emails%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20yous.%26quot%3B%20If%20I%20don't%20hear%20from%20him%20in%20two%20or%20three%20hours%2C%20I'll%20check%20in.%20These%20gestures%20may%20seem%20ordinary%20early%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20but%20after%2035%20years%2C%20they%20have%20added%20up%20to%20something%20extraordinary%3A%20a%20marriage%20built%20on%20daily%20connection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20that%20ongoing%20dialogue%20that%20has%20kept%20us%20emotionally%20close%20and%20prevented%20misunderstandings%20from%20festering%20into%20resentment.%20We've%20had%20very%20few%20big%20conflicts%20over%20the%20course%20of%20our%20marriage%2C%20partly%20because%20we%20share%20the%20same%20values%20and%20outlook.%20And%20when%20we%20don't%2C%20we%20talk%20about%20it%20until%20we%20find%20common%20ground.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255a9f23e-9304-45a7-9793-d6726774aaaa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20give%20each%20other%20room%20to%20grow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20three%20and%20a%20half%20decades%20together%2C%20both%20of%20us%20have%20changed%20in%20ways%20we%20never%20could%20have%20predicted.%20Our%20interests%2C%20careers%2C%20and%20even%20personalities%20have%20evolved.%20Instead%20of%20resisting%20those%20changes%2C%20we've%20learned%20to%20embrace%20them.%20We%20celebrate%20each%20other's%20achievements%20and%20respect%20each%20other's%20independence%2C%20knowing%20that%20growth%20keeps%20us%20moving%20forward%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20that%20growth%20came%20from%20the%20time%20we%20spent%20as%20a%20couple%20before%20becoming%20parents.%20We%20waited%20much%20longer%20than%20most%20couples%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarried-20-years-before-having-kids-hard-but-right-choice-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edidn't%20have%20children%20until%20we%20were%20in%20our%2040s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20That%20delay%20gave%20us%20years%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20we%20were%20%E2%80%94%20both%20individually%20and%20together%20%E2%80%94%20before%20adding%20kids%20into%20the%20mix.%20Those%20early%20decades%20of%20just%20us%20built%20a%20strong%20foundation%20and%20a%20shared%20identity%20as%20a%20couple%20before%20facing%20parenthood%20together%20and%20discovering%20an%20entirely%20new%20facet%20of%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221bd6c00-c19d-4941-bc15-27a0aafe4021%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20still%20make%20time%20for%20each%20other%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Navy%20years%20are%20behind%20us.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-letting-kids-sleep-screentime-do-nothing-summer-break-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20two%20teenagers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20Jay%20is%2010%20years%20into%20a%20teaching%20career.%20Even%20now%2C%20with%20busy%20careers%20and%20family%20life%2C%20we%20carve%20out%20time%20just%20for%20us.%20It%20doesn't%20take%20a%20big%20getaway%20(though%20I%20wouldn't%20say%20no%20if%20someone%20wanted%20to%20wrangle%20our%20teens%20and%20pets%20for%20a%20week)%20%E2%80%94%20often%2C%20it's%20a%20short%20drive%20to%20run%20errands%2C%20a%20weekend%20coffee%20date%2C%20or%20chatting%20after%20dinner%20or%20before%20bed%20about%20our%20day%20and%20what's%20coming%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20also%20talk%20about%20the%20future.%20We%20talk%20about%20what%20our%20lives%20will%20look%20like%20when%20our%20kids%20are%20in%20college%2C%20what%20we'll%20do%20when%20we%20are%20retired%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-allow-teens-have-